# Global Locale Selection

When content language is Russian:
Use locale-ru.mdc.

When content language is English:
Use locale-en.mdc.

When content language is German:
Use locale-de.mdc.

When content language is French:
Use locale-fr.mdc.

When content language is Spanish:
Use locale-es.mdc.

When content language is Portuguese:
Use locale-pt.mdc.

Never mix formatting conventions between locales.
